      <groundspeak:short_description html="True">&lt;b&gt;22 May 2026, 16:30 - 17:00&lt;/b&gt;</groundspeak:short_description>
      <groundspeak:long_description html="True">&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-size:16px;"&gt;itwasmymouse and I are adventuring through Nebraska as we make our way toward the legendary GeoWoodstock XXII in Hutchinson, Kansas.  Before we finish our trek for the day, we’re hosting a quick afternoon meet-up at the Lincoln McDonald&amp;#39;s. We’d love to connect with the local community while grabbing a quick drink or snack.  (No purchase necessary)  Come share some &amp;quot;Husker&amp;quot; hospitality and geocaching stories with us!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;

